model.implementation.analysis

Class GeneratedPopulationComposition

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.implementation.analysis.GeneratedPopulationComposition
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StatisticalTables, PopulationInformationCollection

    public class GeneratedPopulationComposition
extends java.lang.Object
implements PopulationInformationCollection, StatisticalTables
    The GeneratedPopulationComposition interface provides the functionality to be able to access the same information about the simulated population as in the provided population. It also provides methods to retrieve data in the forms required for the various statistical analyses that are used in the verification of the produced population.
